@startuml
autonumber
actor Admin
participant "Product Form (UI)" as UI
participant "ProductController" as Controller
participant "ProductService" as Service
database "Product DB" as DB_Product
database "ProductDiscount DB" as DB_Discount

== Bi-directional Pricing Calculation on Frontend ==
Admin -> UI: Input original price (basePrice)
Admin -> UI: Select discountType (PERCENTAGE / FIXED_AMOUNT)

alt Case A: Admin inputs discountValue (e.g., 10% or 50,000)
    UI -> UI: calculate salePrice = basePrice - discount
    UI -> UI: Display calculated "Giá sau giảm mong muốn"
else Case B: Admin inputs target salePrice directly
    UI -> UI: calculate discountValue based on target salePrice
    UI -> UI: Auto-fill discountValue input field
end

== Save / Update Product Discount ==
Admin -> UI: Click "Save Product"
activate UI

UI -> Controller: POST/PUT /api/admin/products (productDetails & discountDetails)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: saveProductWithDiscount(productData, discountData)
activate Service

Service -> DB_Product: Save / Update Product (name, base price, etc.)
activate DB_Product
DB_Product --> Service: Return updated product (productId)
deactivate DB_Product

alt Discount Details provided
    Service -> DB_Discount: Update / Create ProductDiscount\n(productId, type, value, dates, isStackable)
    activate DB_Discount
    DB_Discount --> Service: Return discount record
    deactivate DB_Discount
else No Discount details
    Service -> DB_Discount: Deactivate existing discounts for productId
end

Service --> Controller: Return saved product status
deactivate Service

Controller --> UI: Response 200 OK / Success
deactivate Controller

UI --> Admin: Show success toast notification & redirect
deactivate UI
@enduml
